sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant SPA as Angular SPA
    participant PF as PingFederate AS
    participant Plugin as BankingTransferProcessor (Plugin JAR)
    participant Core as Core Banking API

    User->>SPA: Initiate payment transfer
    SPA->>PF: GET /as/authorize?authorization_details=[{type:banking_transfer,...}]
    PF->>User: Display login form
    User->>PF: Submit credentials

    PF->>Plugin: Invoke processor with authorization_details + user attributes
    Plugin->>Core: GET /api/users/{uid}/status
    Core-->>Plugin: { blocked: false }
    Plugin->>Core: GET /api/ibans/{iban}/status
    Core-->>Plugin: { frozen: false }

    alt All checks passed
        Plugin-->>PF: Authorization granted
        PF->>SPA: Redirect with auth_code
        SPA->>PF: POST /as/token.oauth2 (code)
        PF-->>SPA: access_token (JWT with authorization_details)
        SPA->>SPA: Payment flow continues
    else Check failed
        Plugin-->>PF: Authorization denied
        PF-->>SPA: error=access_denied
        SPA->>User: Display error (no token issued)
    end
